  //  returned. Otherwise, FALSE is returned with dwError set to one of the
  //  following:
  //      CRYPT_E_NO_VERIFY_USAGE_DLL
  //      CRYPT_E_NO_VERIFY_USAGE_CHECK
  //      CRYPT_E_VERIFY_USAGE_OFFLINE
