  //+=========================================================================
  //  Simplified Cryptographic Message Data Structures and APIs
  //==========================================================================

  //+-------------------------------------------------------------------------
  //              Conventions for the *pb and *pcb output parameters:
  //
  //              Upon entry to the function:
